and finally, the reference guide, Sustainable
Financing of Protected Areas,

151
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:19,580
A Global Review of Challenges and Options.

152
00:10:19,580 --> 00:10:21,540
We have reached the end of this episode.

153
00:10:21,540 --> 00:10:24,160
I suggest you have a look at the reference
materials

154
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:27,390
and I wish you a good day.

